      <url>/2023/03/12/Java%E6%98%93%E9%94%99%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="java易错总结"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#java易错总结">#</a> <strong>java 易错总结</strong></h1><h2 id="1字符串"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#1字符串">#</a> 1. 字符串</h2><p>String str = scanner.next ();接收字符串用.next () 或.nextLine ()</p><table><thead><tr><th></th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>next</td><td>1. 不能接收空格，只能得到不带空格的字符串<br>2. 读到有效字符后才会将空格、Tab、Enter 视为结束符</td></tr><tr><td>nextLine</td><td>1. 可以接收空格，得到带空格的字符串<br>2.nextLine () 将 Enter 视为结束</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="数组"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#数组">#</a> 数组</h2><h3 id="定义数组"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#定义数组">#</a> 定义数组</h3><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> a[][] = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">int</span> [n][n];</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
